quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  21,29,"Oyo yenna mubo agamba nti mazima nze ndi Katonda naaleka Katonda omu, oyo tugenda kumusasula omuliro Jahannama. Bwe tutyo bwe tusasula abeeyisa obubi"
  21,30,Abo abaakaafuwala tebakiraba nti mazima eggulu omusanvu n'ensi byali kitole netubyabuluzaamu era netuggya mu mazzi buli kintu ekiramu abaffe tebakkiriza
  21,31,Era netussa mu nsi ensozi ebe nga tebayuuza era netussa mu yo amakubo kibayambe okumanya gye balaga
  21,32,"Era netufuula eggulu akasolya akakuumibwa, wabula bbo tebafaayo ku bya magero bya byo (ebya byonna ebyogeddwa waggulu)"
  21,33,Era (Katonda) yye yooyo eyatonda ekiro n'emisana n'enjuba n'omwezi buli kimu kiri mu bbanga (nga byonna) biwuga
  21,34,"Era tetuwanga muntu yenna oluberyeberyelwo buwangaazi obw'olubeerera, bwoba ofudde bo be b'okubeerawo olubeerera"
  21,35,Buli muntu wa kukomba ku kufa era tubagezesa n'obubi n'obulungi nga kikemo era gye tuli gye mulizzibwa
  21,36,Abaakaafuwala bwe bakulaba tebakufuula okugyako eky'omuzannyo (ne bagamba) nti ono y'oyo ayogera ku bye musinza nga nabo bawakanya okwogera ku Katonda ow'ekisa ekingi
  21,37,Omuntu yatondebwa nga ayanguyiriza nja ku balaga obubonerero bwange kale temunsaba kubanguyiriza bibonerezo
  21,38,Era abakaafiiri bagamba nti ekiragaanyiso ekyo kiribaawo ddi bwe muba nga mwogera mazima
  21,39,"Abo abaakaafuwala singa bamanyi (ekiribaawo) mu kiseera we batalisobolera kuziyiza muliro kutuuka ku byenyi bya bwe wadde e migongo gya bwe, era nga tebagenda kutaasibwa"
  21,40,"Wabula biribatuukako kibwatukira nebibakanga, tebalisobola kubizzayo era si baakulindirizibwa"
  21,41,"Mazima ababaka (bangi) baagyejebwa olubereberyelwo, nebituuka ku abo abaabanyoomanga ebyo bye baalinga bajeeja. (Abo abaali babajeeja baatuukibwako ebibonerezo bye baali bajeeja)"
  21,42,Bagambe nti ani abakuuma ekiro n'emisana okubawonya ekyandibatuseeko okuva ewa Katonda ow'ekisa ekingi wabula bbo abatakkiriza beesamba okwogera ku Mukama omulabirizi waabwe
  21,43,Abaffe balina ba katonda abalibawonya ku ffe abatali ffe (ba katonda baabwe bennyini) tebagenda kusobola kwetaasa era tebagenda kufuna gwe baliba naye abawonya ku ffe
  21,44,"Wabula twabawa bo ne bakitaabwe okweyagala, okutuusa obuwangaazi lwe bwabawanvuwako, abaffe tebalaba nti mazima ffe, tuddira ensi netugikendeeza okuva ku nsalo zaayo abaffe bo be b'okulema"
  21,45,"Bagambe nti mazima mbatiisa nga nkozesa obubaka, wabula ba kiggala tebawulira kukoowoola bwe baba balabuddwa"
  21,46,So nga bwe balituukwako akatundu ku bibonerezo bya Mukama omulabiriziwo bagenda kugambira ddala nti zitusanze mazima ffe tubadde tweyisa bubi
  21,47,"Tugenda kussaawo minzane entuufu ezirikozesebwa ku lunaku lw'enkomerero, olwo nno tewali muntu aliryazaamaanyizibwa kintu kyonna, ne bwe kiriba kyenkana obuzito bwe mpeke ya khardali tugenda kukireeta. Kimala bumazi okuba nti ffe tuliba ababazi"
  21,48,Twawa Musa ne Haruna amateeka (Taurat) agaawula wakati wa mazima n'obulimba era nga kitangaaala era nga kya kubuulirira eri abatya Katonda
  21,49,Abo abatya Mukama omulabirizi waabwe awamu n'okuba nga tebamulaba era nga nabo beeraliikirira ekiseera ky'enkomerero
  21,50,"Eno (k’urane) kubuulirira okw'omukisa kwe twassa, abaffe mugiwakanya"